#: ../../source/SDKManual/sdk_use.rst:3
msgid "SDK客户端动态库使用"
msgstr "SDK Client Dynamic Library Usage"

#: ../../source/SDKManual/sdk_use.rst:9
msgid ""
"SDK库的使用需要在上位机上，SDK库会通过TCP连接与机器人控制器建立通讯，推荐使用Ubuntu系统，Windows系统暂时不支持。执行SDK所需要的文件目录如下所示。"
msgstr ""
"Using the SDK library requires a host computer, where the SDK establishes "
"communication with the robot controller via TCP connection. Ubuntu is "
"recommended; Windows is currently unsupported. The required file directory "
"for executing the SDK is shown below."

#: ../../source/SDKManual/sdk_use.rst:-1
msgid "004.png"
msgstr "004.png"

#: ../../source/SDKManual/sdk_use.rst:16
msgid "图表 2-1 SDK库目录"
msgstr "Figure 2-1 SDK Library Directory"

#: ../../source/SDKManual/sdk_use.rst:18
msgid ""
"注意事项： "
"1.注意需要将libfairino_middleware_logger、libfairino_motion_planner和libkine_FR_7Axis动态库与libhumanorid_sdk动态库放到同一文件目录下。"
msgstr ""
"Note: 1. Ensure that the dynamic libraries libfairino_middleware_logger, "
"libfairino_motion_planner, and libkine_FR_7Axis are placed in the same "
"directory as the libhumanorid_sdk dynamic library."
